--- RESULT ---
All 8 Astro pages were created successfully and the build passed with zero errors (1423 pages generated).

**Pages created:**

- **`src/pages/compare.astro`** — Fully client-side comparison tool: 2-4 product slots with autocomplete search from a slim inlined product index, URL state (`?a=...&b=...`), add/remove slots, Compare button rendering a full spec table with green/red winner highlighting, auto-summary ("X wins in Y out of Z spec categories"), and Share button (copies URL).

- **`src/pages/news.astro`** — News listing using `NewsCard` components, sorted by date descending, with horizontal scrollable source filter pills (All, Androidauthority, Engadget, Theverge, Techcrunch, 9To5Google, Hacker News). Live count updates on filter change.

- **`src/pages/about.astro`** — About page with feature overview, data source info (GSMArena, Wikidata), AI-generated content disclaimer, and coverage stats.

- **`src/pages/contact.astro`** — Contact page with a feedback form (name, email, subject dropdown, message), email/GitHub contact cards.

- **`src/pages/privacy.astro`** — Privacy policy: no personal data collection, cookies for preferences, affiliate link tracking, third-party services (CDNs, Google Fonts, GitHub Pages).

- **`src/pages/terms.astro`** — Terms of service: free personal use, data accuracy disclaimer, AI content warning, affiliate disclosure link, limitation of liability, IP notice.

- **`src/pages/disclosure.astro`** — FTC-compliant affiliate disclosure: Amazon Associates, Flipkart Affiliate, explanation that commissions don't affect prices or editorial content.

- **`src/pages/404.astro`** — Glass-card styled 404 page with large 404 heading, search bar (reuses SearchBar component), and quick links to homepage/compare/news.

All pages use `BaseLayout`, Tailwind dark theme classes consistent with the existing design, and all internal links use the `/phonehub` base path.
